OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCountdown: Anne Robinson to
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fstep down as presenter     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Anne Robinson is stepping down as the  
OL,6, host of Channel 4 quiz show Countdown  
OL,7, after a year.                          
OL,9,FThe former Weakest Link presenter, 77, 
OL,10,Fjoined the daytime staple in 2021,     
OL,11,Fbecoming its sixth presenter and the   
OL,12,Ffirst woman to take the role.          
OL,14,FShe said she had a "blast" hosting the 
OL,15,Fshow but it was now time for "an older 
OL,16,Fwoman to take the reins".              
OL,18,FRobinson, who recorded 265 episodes,   
OL,19,Fwill appear in shows until the summer, 
OL,20,FChannel 4 said.                        
